abstract = {Our research theme is evolving around the concept of computer profiling. The aim of our work is to propose an approach that will detect web profiles in a unique way and to model a print web for each profile. Our main concern is to find this signature from text messages in the forums, by analyzing the vocabulary used by each user. Also we will focus here on presenting our approach and our future work in a way that will allow us to detect the "Specific Vocabulary" for each web profile.},
